description:
In this JamSnack, you'll learn what's new in Next.js. Next expert Cassidy Williams talks about exciting updates for the project, including some of their favorite features such as React Fast Refresh and new ways to build with Next on Netlify package. 

Learn more about Next.js: https://nextjs.org/, https://jamstack.org/generators/next/

Presented by Cassidy Williams, Principal Developer Experience Engineer at Netlify, https://github.com/cassidoo , https://twitter.com/cassidoo , https://cassidoo.co/

Brought to you by Netlify (netlify.com) - Jamstack Conf Virtual 2020 https://jamstackconf.com
title: JamSnack - What's New in Next.js
